description._content: Description: 3. Fully stocked stand of Aleppo pine in southern range fulfilling all objects of management. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Description: 4. Typical forest in southern range showing range showing well stocked forest in foreground and more open forest at the back. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
